## Tips before your cleaning visit in Ganderbal

- **Clear clutter** from floors and surfaces you want cleaned thoroughly.
- **Note fragile items**, locked rooms, or areas to skip.
- **Secure pets** if needed, and share access instructions.
- **For move-in or post-renovation jobs**, mention dust or construction debris in advance.
- **Be home or arrange access** so the team can start on time.

